mp;utm_campaign=domain_click" data-visit-website-button-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xxs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Button_buttonText__7e7b1d">Visitar el sitio web<span class="CDS_Button_iconSpan__7e7b1d"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_inherit__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 2H2v12h12V8h-1v5H3V3h5V2Zm2 1h2.293L7.646 7.646l.708.708L13 3.707V6h1V2h-4v1Z"/></svg></span></span></a></div></div></div></section><div class="styles_mobile__tu1C7"><a name="write-review-button" class="CDS_Button_button__7e7b1d CDS_Button_m__7e7b1d CDS_Button_appearance-primary__7e7b1d CDS_Button_wide__7e7b1d CDS_Button_iconLeft__7e7b1d" rel="nofollow noopener" href="/evaluate/spliff.fr" data-write-review-button-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xxs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Button_buttonText__7e7b1d"><span class="CDS_Button_iconSpan__7e7b1d"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_inherit__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M16 2.713 13.288 0l-1.567 1.567-9.564 9.56L0 15.996l4.934-2.223 9.145-9.14L16 2.714Zm-2.274.86.86-.86-1.298-1.3-.86.86 1.298 1.3ZM1.962 14.034l1.75-.776-.974-.975-.776 1.751Zm2.62-1.32-1.3-1.3 8.438-8.433L13.02 4.28 4.58 12.714Z"/></svg></span>Escribir una opinión</span></a></div></div><div class="styles_businessInfoColumnBottom__Qfl3B"><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_appearance-default__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a variant_container__05pif styles_accordionCard__OxNnf" data-review-incentives-banner-variant-accordion="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681" weight="heavy"><button aria-controls="review-incentives-banner-variant-panel" aria-expanded="false" class="variant_button__IC5Ps" id="review-incentives-banner-variant"><span class="styles_trustShieldLogo__WGwe_"><img alt="" src="https://businessunitprofile-cdn.trustpilot.net/businessunitprofile-consumersite/public/trustpilot-shield.svg" width="25" height="30" class="styles_trustShieldImg__z4P_B"/><span class="styles_animation__QNRFp"></span></span><div class="styles_titleContainer__nh3Z4"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xxs__68c681">Usamos tecnología para proteger la integridad de la plataforma pero no comprobamos la información de las opiniones</span></div><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_default__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="m8.003 10.289 5.617-6.557.76.65-6.377 7.444L1.62 4.383l.76-.651 5.623 6.557Z"/></svg></button></h2><section aria-labelledby="review-incentives-banner-variant" class="variant_content__GcvGt variant_contentPadding__q_JrG" id="review-incentives-banner-variant-panel"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681">Aunque no verificamos reclamaciones concretas porque las opiniones son propiedad de sus autores, es posible que marquemos las opiniones como «verificadas» si podemos confirmar que ha tenido lugar una interacción con la empresa. <a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-action__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_underline__0e2efd" data-testid="review-incentives-learn-more-link-1" href="https://help.trustpilot.com/s/article/Trustpilots-review-labels?language=es" target="_blank" data-name="trustpilots-review-labels-link">Más información</a></p><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_secondParagraph__Hgl7m">Para proteger la integridad de la plataforma, nuestro software automatizado disponible las 24 horas examina todas las opiniones en nuestra plataforma, tanto si están verificadas como si no. Esta tecnología está diseñada para identificar y eliminar contenido que incumpla nuestras directrices, incluidas las opiniones que no están basadas en una experiencia real. Sabemos que es posible que no detectemos todo pero puedes denunciar lo que pienses que se nos haya escapado. <a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-action__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_underline__0e2efd" data-testid="review-incentives-learn-more-link-2" href="https://help.trustpilot.com/s/article/How-consumers-can-flag-reviews-that-breach-our-guidelines?language=es" target="_blank" data-name="how-consumers-can-flag-reviews-that-breach-our-guidelines-link">Más información</a></p></section></div><div class="styles_companyDetails__30xkf" data-business-unit-about-section="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-m__68c681">Información sobre la empresa</h2><div class="styles_detailsWrapper__3QFeh"><ol class="styles_flexRow__eqdt3"><li class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 styles_category__8f4_m" data-business-unit-info-category-typography="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-action__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/categories/cannabis_store">Tienda de cannabis</a></li><li><span><span role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Tooltip" data-testid="tooltip-element" data-state="closed"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650" style="fill:#6C6C85" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 1a7 7 0 1 0 0 14A7 7 0 0 0 8 1ZM0 8a8 8 0 1 1 16 0A8 8 0 0 1 0 8Z"/><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7.5 7h-.75V6H8.5v5.502h.75v1h-2.5v-1h.75V7ZM6.75 4a1 1 0 1 1 2 0 1 1 0 0 1-2 0Z"/></svg></span></span></li></ol><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_appearance-default__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-l__146e7a CDS_Card_padding-m__146e7a styles_companyDetailsCard__k6mCF" data-testid="company-details-card"><div class="styles_overflowContainer__ft5Si"><h3 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_heading__PsO3E styles_headingMargin__eF5iA">Acerca de Spliff</h3><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 styles_subHeading__Qc1aT">Escrito por la empresa</p><div class="styles_container__NG5iv customer-generated-content" data-html-block="true"><a href="https://www.spliff.fr" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Spliff</a>
 offre une expérience exceptionnelle dans le monde du CBD récréatif. Des fleurs de qualité premium et des produits décontractés qui font de chaque moment une escapade chill. 🌿💨 #SpliffVibes</div></div></div></div><hr class="CDS_Divider_divider__474617 CDS_Divider_subtle__474617 styles_mobile__tu1C7"/><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-m__68c681">Información de contacto</h2><ul class="styles_itemsColumn__N6BEW"><li class="styles_itemRow__74s4a"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_default__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16px" role="img"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M3.404 1.904A6.5 6.5 0 0 1 14.5 6.5v.01c0 .194 0 .396-.029.627l-.004.03-.023.095c-.267 2.493-1.844 4.601-3.293 6.056a18.723 18.723 0 0 1-2.634 2.19 11.015 11.015 0 0 1-.234.154l-.013.01-.004.002h-.002L8 15.25l-.261.426h-.002l-.004-.003-.014-.009a13.842 13.842 0 0 1-.233-.152 18.388 18.388 0 0 1-2.64-2.178c-1.46-1.46-3.05-3.587-3.318-6.132l-.003-.026v-.068c-.025-.2-.025-.414-.025-.591V6.5a6.5 6.5 0 0 1 1.904-4.596ZM8 15.25l-.261.427.263.16.262-.162L8 15.25Zm-.002-.598a17.736 17.736 0 0 0 2.444-2.04c1.4-1.405 2.79-3.322 3.01-5.488l.004-.035.026-.105c.018-.153.018-.293.018-.484a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-11 0c0 .21.001.371.02.504l.005.035v.084c.24 2.195 1.632 4.109 3.029 5.505a17.389 17.389 0 0 0 2.444 2.024Z"/><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M8 4a2.5 2.5 0 1 0 0 5 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5ZM4.5 6.5a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 7 0 3.5 3.5 0 0 1-7 0Z"/></svg><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681">42 rue de l&#x27;aiguillerie, 34000, Montpellier, Francia</p></li><li class="styles_itemRow__74s4a"><svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="CDS_Icon_icon__96d650 CDS_Icon_default__96d650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16px" height="16p