ography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Maravilloso</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Maravilloso </p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">29 de julio de 2025</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Opinión espontánea</span></div></div></div></div></section></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Información sobre customer"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_avatar__dd7fc3 CDS_Avatar_green__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;min-width:44px;height:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Avatar_avatarName__dd7fc3">CU</span></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/6183f70c4a974d0012c1511f" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">customer</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="7"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">ES</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">7<!-- --> opiniones</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2024-12-16T15:32:37.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">Actualizada el 16 dic 2024</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="3"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Valorada con 3 estrellas sobre 5" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-3.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/6750eec073969a8ba87e4f1c" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Pedido 13242</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">10 días laborables en llegar el pedido, tal vez para los que residan fuera de Francia los tiempos sean un hándicap para ser clientes recurrentes.<br/>Pedí un total de 9 hash, he de decir que la ejecución es bastante buena pero la intensidad del sabor y el olor es bastante flojo, las flores de cbd no suelen tener la potencia de sus primas Thc pero en este sentido las hay mejores. Los niveles de cbd o cbn no corresponden con el efecto, tal vez una analítica con valores de sus cannabinoides daría más fiabilidad al cliente y caché a la empresa.<br/>Los que más me gustaron.. <br/>-Black cristal, de textura dura pero es auténtica resina, poco sabor/olor y efecto muy suave para su 85% de Cbn<br/>-Static runtz, aunque llegó arena el sabor y olor es rico aunque también flojo, de efecto muy suave también.<br/>Los que menos me gustaron...<br/>GMO Y static hash, malos, si fumas 1gr dan náuseas y cierto malestar, no recomiendo además el efecto es inexistente.<br/>Mantengo las 3 estrellas por tiempos de envío y flores, hay proveedores con productos que supuestamente continenen menos cbd y hacen más efecto, además tienen sabores y olores más potentes. Aún así no están mal pero no valen su precio, no creo que repita.<br/><br/> </p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">5 de diciembre de 2024</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Opinión espontánea</span></div></div></div></div></section></div></article></div><div id="hotjar-survey-container" class="styles_hotjarSurveyContainer__0E92X"></div></div><a name="show-all-reviews" class="CDS_Button_button__7e7b1d CDS_Button_l__7e7b1d CDS_Button_appearance-secondary__7e7b1d styles_link__jtkno" rel="nofollow" data-show-all-reviews-button="true" href="/review/spliff.fr?languages=all"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Button_buttonText__7e7b1d">Mostrar opiniones en todos los idiomas. (<!-- -->512<!-- --> opiniones)</span></a><div><nav data-cpl="true" role="navigation" aria-label="Paginación" class="pagination_pagination__K4LuV"><a data-cpl="true" tabindex="-1" aria-disabled="true" rel="prev" name="pagination-button-previous" target="_self" aria-label="Página anterior" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_disabled__vpJqK button_button__EM6gX button_m__J8iy5 button_appearance-outline__K_fYw button_squared__ApvnR link_button__5LH_w pagination-link_buttonItem__BQ0JJ pagination-link_prev__Do_jK pagination-link_disabled__UYSG0" data-pagination-name="pagination-button-previous" data-pagination-button-previous-link="true"><span data-cpl="true" class="typography_prettyStyle__eq6jq typography_heading-xxs__UmE9o typography_appearance-inherit__YnCNb typography_disableResponsiveSizing__z3EGy">Anterior</span></a><a data-cpl="true" href="/review/spliff.fr" name="pagination-button-1" target="_self" aria-label="Número de página 1" aria-current="page" class="link_internal__Ea